  "title": "Senior Finance Executive",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><ul><li>Report to Managing Director, Deputy Director & Senior Manager (Shared Services)</li><li>Performs full set of accounts</li><li>Handle / Support in Payroll Preparation</li><li>Perform bank reconciliation</li><li>Preparation of progress claims and submission to client</li><li>Prepare month end closing</li><li>Prepare cashflow projection & budgeting for each project</li><li>Prepare monthly management report, yearly budget and profitability analysis</li><li>Liaising with external auditor and tax agent</li><li>Preparation, Filling, and Submission of CPF, GST and tax return</li><li>Checking stand in payment and provide costing advice</li><li>Prepare and process invoices</li><li>Prepare cashflow projection analysis</li><li>Manage bank loan, facility and hire purchase</li><li>Oversee Finance Executive</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma or professional qualifications in accountancy</li><li>Min 4 years of accounting experience, advantageous if possess experience in construction industry</li><li>Able to multi task and work with cross departments</li><li>Able to work and deliver under pressure and tight dateline</li><li>Able to work independently with minimal supervision</li><li>Possess good and positive working attitude</li></ul>",
